# Cloudflare Pages / Netlify response headers.
# Cross-origin isolation → crossOriginIsolated → SharedArrayBuffer → multithreaded WASM.
# COEP=credentialless (not require-corp) so the cross-origin CDN/HF imports
# (jsdelivr libraries + HuggingFace models, incl. titanet.onnx) still load.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless
